data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning residence offers an abundance of space, featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and an upstairs loft. Situated on a spacious lot, this property provides the ultimate privacy, with a serene conservation area as its backdrop and no rear neighbors.Prepare to be enchanted as you enter this extraordinary dwelling. The home has laminate floors and an updated kitchen that will leave you in awe. Boasting shaker style cabinets, granite countertops, recessed lighting, and stainless-steel appliances, this kitchen is perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Its open layout seamlessly connects to the dining area and family room, creating a harmonious space for entertaining and relaxation. The exterior of this home has been freshly painted. The master bedroom features two walk-in closets and a spacious bathroom complete with a garden tub, separate shower, and double sinks. Upstairs, you will find two additional bedrooms, a loft area, and another bathroom, while downstairs offers an additional bedroom and bathroom for added convenience. Step outside onto the expansive tiled patio with a fully fenced yard, where you can host unforgettable gatherings or simply unwind while enjoying the breathtaking views of the lush wooded conservation area. Located in the highly sought-after East Orlando, this home is just minutes away from the Waterford Lakes Shopping Center, OIA, UCF, a variety of dining options, and major highways. An elementary school around the corner is also conveniently close by. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity - schedule your showing today!
